item.title: Git常见错误
item.description: 一、fatal: unable to access ‘https://github.com/baer9/baer9.github.io.git/': OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054 解除ssl验证 解决：关闭验证 git config –global http.sslVerify “false” 二、fatal: unable to access ‘https://github.com/baer9/baer9.github.io.git/': Failed to connect to github.com port 443: Timed out 文件可能太大 解决：gi
